query: SELECT cd.id, cd.documentType, cd.fileUrl FROM customerDocuments cd JOIN proposals p ON cd.customerId = p.customerId WHERE p.id = 540001 AND cd.documentType IN ('switchboard_photo', 'meter_photo', 'roof_photo', 'property_photo') LIMIT 10;
